- Got it!

00:23:23.120 --> 00:23:24.240
This is unacceptable!

00:23:24.320 --> 00:23:26.560
Get your CEO out here now!

00:23:26.640 --> 00:23:29.400
Unacceptable! Give it back!

00:23:29.480 --> 00:23:30.800
Give us our money back!

00:23:30.880 --> 00:23:32.200
Hey! Give it back!

00:23:32.800 --> 00:23:35.120
{\an8}Let us talk to your CEO now!

00:23:35.200 --> 00:23:36.400
{\an8}We won't stand for this!

00:23:36.480 --> 00:23:38.360
Get your CEO out here now!

00:23:38.440 --> 00:23:40.320
- Guys, please stop. Please calm down
- Unacceptable!

00:23:40.400 --> 00:23:41.640
- Give it back!
- Please stop.

00:23:41.720 --> 00:23:42.800
Give us our money back!

00:23:42.880 --> 00:23:45.840
