00:24:25.320 --> 00:24:28.280
If you had to travel while worrying,
"Do I have COVID, or do you?",

00:24:28.360 --> 00:24:30.280
that'd be no fun, right?

00:24:30.360 --> 00:24:33.680
So, today, I have
a great offer for you guys.

00:24:33.760 --> 00:24:35.360
We'll all die one day.

00:24:36.360 --> 00:24:37.200
- What?
- Huh?

00:24:37.280 --> 00:24:39.280
But we should die of old age.

00:24:39.360 --> 00:24:41.960
We won't die because of COVID.

00:24:42.040 --> 00:24:43.920
- Ah.
- Ah.

00:24:44.000 --> 00:24:45.120
When you're traveling,

00:24:45.200 --> 00:24:48.440
