if you test positive for COVID.

00:25:01.760 --> 00:25:04.360
Normally, you'd need to buy
this package separately,

00:25:04.440 --> 00:25:06.360
but for everyone on this trip,

00:25:06.440 --> 00:25:10.040
we're giving it away for free,
no extra charges!

00:25:10.120 --> 00:25:11.560
- Good!
- Great!

00:25:11.640 --> 00:25:13.520
Great, right? Wanna take a look? Here.

00:25:13.600 --> 00:25:15.320
- How interesting.
- Is it good?

00:25:15.400 --> 00:25:16.640
- Interesting.
- Hand 'em out.

00:25:16.720 --> 00:25:18.520
- Please hand them out.
- Oh, right.

00:25:18.600 --> 00:25:20.280
- Wanna go?
- We should go!

00:25:20.360 --> 00:25:21.680
- Here.
- Wow!

00:25:21.760 --> 00:25:23.320
Please take a look.

00:25:23.400 --> 00:25:24.640
Here's the offer.

00:25:24.720 --> 00:25:26.960
- Right here.
- Come on, guys.

00:25:44.840 --> 00:25:46.880
Have a safe drive back home.

00:25:46.960 --> 00:25:49.200
At A Round Trip Travel,
we're happy to be of service.

00:25:56.200 --> 00:25:59.120
At A Round Trip Travel,
we're happy to be of service.

00:26:01.240 --> 00:26:02.560
Thank you, everyone.

00:26:02.640 --> 00:26:03.480
