- Thank you.

00:26:03.560 --> 00:26:05.000
Don't forget, okay?

00:26:05.080 --> 00:26:06.960
Goodbye, everyone.

00:26:07.040 --> 00:26:08.520
Bye-bye.

00:26:16.520 --> 00:26:19.760
Thank you so much
for helping us handle them.

00:26:19.840 --> 00:26:21.200
May I ask you one thing?

00:26:21.280 --> 00:26:23.720
So, who are you?

00:26:25.280 --> 00:26:26.680
My name's Mook.

00:26:26.760 --> 00:26:29.320
Sorry for stepping in like that.

00:26:30.160 --> 00:26:31.120
It's just…

00:26:31.200 --> 00:26:32.480
