00:26:43.920 --> 00:26:45.280
My name's Veluree.

00:26:45.960 --> 00:26:50.080
First of all, I want to apologize
for stepping in uninvited.

00:26:51.040 --> 00:26:53.080
But the situation called for it.

00:26:53.160 --> 00:26:57.080
I had to handle the matter at hand
to please the clients first.

00:26:58.440 --> 00:27:01.160
I happened to find
your company's insurance package,

00:27:01.240 --> 00:27:03.200
so I thought it might help

00:27:03.920 --> 00:27:05.440
because most of the clients

00:27:05.520 --> 00:27:09.000
