about the pandemic and safety.

00:27:09.080 --> 00:27:12.640
So I figured the insurance
would suit their needs.

00:27:13.400 --> 00:27:16.480
That's why I offered to add it for free.

00:27:16.560 --> 00:27:18.000
For free?

00:27:18.920 --> 00:27:19.760
Yes.

00:27:20.280 --> 00:27:22.960
I know quite a bit about insurance costs,

00:27:23.040 --> 00:27:26.080
so I figured it'd be wiser
than cancelling the whole trip.

00:27:26.160 --> 00:27:29.720
I figured you weren't a rookie
in the tourism industry

00:27:29.800 --> 00:27:32.320
because you handled
the clients really well.

00:27:36.040 --> 00:27:37.920
Which company did you work for?

00:27:41.080 --> 00:27:43.280
