00:28:14.960 --> 00:28:15.800
Hold on…

00:28:17.240 --> 00:28:18.360
Here's her car key, Boss.

00:28:19.240 --> 00:28:20.080
- Okay.
- I'd better go.

00:28:20.160 --> 00:28:21.280
- Where are you going,
- Sure.

00:28:21.360 --> 00:28:22.720
- Sue?
- Mook…

00:28:22.800 --> 00:28:24.200
Just taking them home.

00:28:24.280 --> 00:28:25.760
- What?
- Just go home with Boss.

00:28:25.840 --> 00:28:27.200
Aren't they still inside?

00:28:27.280 --> 00:28:28.280
- They're going home.
- They're wasted.

00:28:28.360 --> 00:28:29.440
They're there now. Let's go.

00:28:31.560 --> 00:28:32.560
The heck, man?

00:28:35.280 --> 00:28:38.200
Mook, I'm taking you home, okay?

00:28:39.200 --> 00:28:40.800
Oh, Boss!

00:28:43.080 --> 00:28:44.640
Why are you so late?

00:28:46.000 --> 00:28:48.000
Come on. Let's get you home.

00:28:48.080 --> 00:28:50.160
Home who?!

00:28:50.240 --> 00:28:52.040
I'm not even wasted yet.

00:28:52.120 --> 00:28:53.920
Come on. Let's keep partyin'.

00:28:54.000 --> 00:28:55.640
- Let's sing some karaoke.
- Mook!

00:28:57.480 --> 00:28:58.960
Come on. Let's go home.

00:28:59.040 --> 00:29:00.680
I'm not going!

00:29:01.640 --> 00:29:02.760
Fine then, Mook.

00:29:02.840 --> 00:29:04.400
Let's go to another bar, okay?

00:29:04.480 --> 00:29:05.840
- Another bar?
- Yeah.

00:29:05.920 --> 00:29:06.760
Let's go.

00:29:06.840 --> 00:29:08.960
- Come on.
- You sure You can keep up, Boss?

00:29:09.040 --> 00:29:10.320
Of course. Here, get on my back.

00:29:10.400 --> 00:29:11.880
- On your back?!
- Yeah.

00:29:11.960 --> 00:29:13.520
- Boss, you rock!
- Hop on.

00:29:13.600 --> 00:29:14.640
Okay.

00:29:16.360 --> 00:29:17.600
- Go!
- Ready?

00:29:17.680 --> 00:29:21.120
Yeah! Go, Boss, go!

00:29:21.200 --> 00:29:22.440
To another bar!

00:29:24.720 --> 00:29:26.200
Go!

00:29:26.280 --> 00:29:27.280
Go, go!

00:29:27.360 --> 00:29:28.680
- Here.
- Go!

00:29:28.760 --> 00:29:29.800
- Mook, Mook!
- Hey!

00:29:29.880 --> 00:29:31.240
- Go, go!
- Mook.

