"Where did I go wrong?

00:29:56.640 --> 00:29:57.960
The love we had…

00:29:58.720 --> 00:30:00.640
When did it go away?

00:30:01.200 --> 00:30:04.480
It used to be just us two
in this rose-colored world,

00:30:04.560 --> 00:30:08.320
then suddenly many people
started to step in,

00:30:08.400 --> 00:30:11.040
causing our love to fall apart."

00:30:11.600 --> 00:30:13.520
When two people stop loving each other,

00:30:13.600 --> 00:30:16.160
it isn't anybody's fault.

00:30:16.240 --> 00:30:19.360
You can cry. Let it out

00:30:19.440 --> 00:30:21.040
- if it…
- Yeah!

00:30:23.760 --> 00:30:26.720
Why does it have to be this way, huh?

00:30:28.160 --> 00:30:29.680
Where did I go wrong?

00:30:43.640 --> 00:30:44.800
Don't turn it off!

00:30:49.440 --> 00:30:51.840
I tried to be a good wife…

00:30:53.000 --> 00:30:55.040
Tried to be a good mom…

00:30:57.400 --> 00:30:59.520
I did everything to change myself.

00:31:01.720 --> 00:31:04.080
I put up with things I never could before.

00:31:05.200 --> 00:31:07.720
And even did things I never did before.

00:31:09.120 --> 00:31:11.880
But it's never enough, Boss.

00:31:12.800 --> 00:31:13.800
And what happens?

00:31:14.320 --> 00:31:16.600
In the end, it's still my fault.

00:31:35.480 --> 00:31:36.640
Mook.

00:31:37.880 --> 00:31:39.040
Please calm down.

00:31:40.600 --> 00:31:41.880
I know how you feel.

00:31:44.600 --> 00:31:46.920
When two people stop loving each other,

00:31:47.000 --> 00:31:48.880
it isn't anybody's fault.

00:31:49.920 --> 00:31:52.720
Enough! Enough is enough!

00:31:52.800 --> 00:31:54.160
Stop talking already!

00:31:55.800 --> 00:31:59.040
You can cry. Let it out…

00:31:59.720 --> 00:32:01.720
I said enough! Stop it!

00:32:02.360 --> 00:32:04.320
I don't wanna hear it.

00:32:05.720 --> 00:32:07.560
You wouldn't understand me, Aod.

00:32:08.160 --> 00:32:10.440
No one understands me.

00:32:13.120 --> 00:32:15.200
No one understands me…

00:33:53.240 --> 00:33:55.640
You have a shareholders' meeting
today, Mr. Thee.

00:35:25.720 --> 00:35:28.840
Ma'am, you're in the wrong room.

00:35:39.160 --> 00:35:40.880
Looks like you had a little too much.

00:35:49.760 --> 00:35:50.960
Wha-- Hey!

00:36:12.000 --> 00:36:12.840
Hey.

00:36:46.640 --> 00:36:48.360
Just a black coffee, please.

00:36:48.440 --> 00:36:49.880
I don't feel like eating today.

00:36:49.960 --> 00:36:50.880
Sure.

00:36:52.160 --> 00:36:54.000
The chairman won't be attending.

00:36:54.080 --> 00:36:55.880
He said you can handle it, Mr. Thee.

00:37:28.520 --> 00:37:31.360
I had your suit dry-cleaned
as you requested, Mr. Thee.

00:38:07.320 --> 00:38:09.840
From what I heard, you completely deserve

00:38:09.920 --> 00:38:14.320
the Young Rising Star CEO Award 2022.

00:38:14.400 --> 00:38:17.280
I'm sure your dad
can enjoy his retirement, huh?

00:38:17.360 --> 00:38:19.760
The company's in good hands now.

00:38:19.840 --> 00:38:20.800
Thank you.

00:38:22.080 --> 00:38:24.000
Thank you all for coming here today.

00:38:24.080 --> 00:38:25.720
I'd like to inform you

00:38:25.800 --> 00:38:30.240
