countries in Southeast Asia.

00:38:35.280 --> 00:38:38.080
And we have been preparing
this action plan for a while.

00:38:40.160 --> 00:38:43.080
The pin location
to expand our line of business…

00:38:43.760 --> 00:38:44.600
