00:39:04.560 --> 00:39:06.200
Morning, everyone.

00:39:06.280 --> 00:39:10.000
- Morning.
- Morning.

00:39:14.160 --> 00:39:16.400
Hey, how'd we get home last night?

00:39:17.240 --> 00:39:21.280
Why do I remember us singing
and then nothing after that?

00:39:32.960 --> 00:39:34.920
Here, Mr. Pat said to give you this.

00:39:38.160 --> 00:39:39.880
SEND 30,000 BAHT FOR LAUNDRY FEE

00:39:41.920 --> 00:39:42.760
Thirty-thousand?!

00:39:46.200 --> 00:39:47.440
This month's commission?

00:39:48.760 --> 00:39:50.200
A laundry fee of 30,000.

00:39:52.120 --> 00:39:53.760
What is this, Mr. Suetrong?

00:39:55.160 --> 00:39:57.280
It's more like compensation.

00:39:57.800 --> 00:39:59.880
Last night, you… puked.

00:40:00.600 --> 00:40:01.840
You puked on some guest,

00:40:01.920 --> 00:40:03.400
so he wanted compensation.

00:40:03.480 --> 00:40:05.160
There's his account number,

00:40:05.240 --> 00:40:06.840
